Tool ID: check_cluster_health_daily
Description: Shows the health status of clusters over the last day, summarizing total counts by status
Labels: cluster-health
Configuration Type: ES|QL

ES|QL Query:

FROM .monitoring-es*
| WHERE type == "cluster_stats"
| WHERE timestamp >= NOW() - 1 DAY
| STATS total = COUNT(*) BY cluster_state.status
| SORT total DESC
| LIMIT 5
